634
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:32,280
Suka...

635
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:38,960
Tentu saja bukan karena suka!

636
00:38:39,080 --> 00:38:40,440
Bukankah Baginda juga pernah bilang?

637
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:42,030
ini hanyalah hubungan antara
Kaisar dan bawahannya.

638
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:54,440
Qingguang,

639
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,280
ayo kita bersama-sama...

640
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,400
melindungi Baginda,

641
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:05,280
bantu dia menyingkirkan
Qiu Ziliang.

642
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:12,520
(Kuil Baikong)

643
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:26,480
Lapor!

644
00:39:28,680 --> 00:39:29,360
Ada apa?

645
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:30,680
Li Zening belum bergerak,

646
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,160
sedangkan Cheng Rouyu
gagal dibuntuti.

647
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,320
Yang ditunggangi Cheng Rouyu
adalah Rufeng,

648
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:36,120
